<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.5">
<l>māṉa vēloṇkaṇ maṭavaral maṇmaka ḷaḻuṅkamun nīrpparappil</l>
<l>ēṉa mākiyaṉ ṟirunila miṭantava ṉēyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>kāṉa māmullai kaḻaikkarum pēṟiveṇ muṟuvalcey talarkiṉṟa</l>
<l>tēṉiṉ vāymalar murukukuk kumtiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Lord] who, as a boar, dug up the vast earth that day from the expanse</l>
<l rend="indent">of the three-watered [ocean],</l>
<l>When lady earth, the simple girl with shining eyes like a proud spear, suffered,</l>
<l rend="indent">grant me grace,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where the blossoms of large forest jasmine,</l>
<l rend="indent">having climbed up sugarcane stalks,</l>
<l>Which bloom resembling white teeth, pour nectar into bees’ mouths.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
